description: Carl Czerny (1791-1857): Variations sur un motif de l'opera La somnambule de Bellini, Op.333, no.2. Vivien Harvey Slater, piano. Like the Czerny variations on The Last Rose of Summer, this set was one Vivien Slater performed a number of times in the 1980's and 1990's. 1980 recording (track 4 of 4).
